Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤…和士？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,本名是叫「和士」么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「可久士」原来是笔名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:34.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的本名是后藤可久士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,日常交际则是用的后藤和士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一不小心就用本名出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为是个比较少见的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤可久士先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您是漫画家么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是这样的事情被姬发现了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:58.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以在那些不重要的卡上我都是写的后藤和士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:02:59.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.66,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz331.6\pos(1003.2,628.8)}出道前·名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.66,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：标题源自喜剧电影「罗马浴场」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们在出道之前也好好想想笔名比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说已经取了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姑且是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,道都还没出呢太狂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,刚刚说让我们想好的不是老师您么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:23.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没关系吧  说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,绝对不说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是绝对不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,深究助手的笔名是万万不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在做什么  姬
