Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:40.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不…不喜欢自己的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家也都说是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姓名解读哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:01.34,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\frz359.5\move(852.8,-165.8,828.4,776,0,7320)}易懂的姓名解读
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.01,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz269.6\c&H824AC0&\move(784.8,287.2,784.8,1056.4,21,5986)}完全版
