Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.42,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\frz359.7\move(1176,250,1188,1059)}工作运\N财运\N恋爱运\N整体运\N\h\h\h\h等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,名字的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在班上很流行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,笔画数不是太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么  给爸爸也来测一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已经测过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,整体运五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,财运五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爱情运五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作运五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有比这更好的笔画了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是  说是不宜从事艺术相关的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H8548D2&\3c&H3C5D9F&\pos(1358.4,22.4)}不宜从事的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1870.4,262.4)}艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1745.6,260.8)\c&H653DD4&}漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1625.6,262.4)}画家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1504,265.6)}书法家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1396.8,262.4)}小说家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1280,265.6)}作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1873.6,576)}插画师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1748.8,582.4)}YouTuber
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1640,584)}V家P主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1520,571.2)}超媒体创作者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸是上班族所以没问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸有个叫这名字的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤和士  孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,似乎是个很可怜的人  所以要好好对待他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是个很可怜的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这  这样么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也非常喜欢小姬的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不仅觉得名字好  最重要的是很好念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:08.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在的孩子  名字不都很难念么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像闪亮亮名字什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.33,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：指那些偏离常识且很珍奇的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:15.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是念错了还会被家长狠狠地训一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,学校的老师经常遇到的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:22.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有  最近取动画漫画角色名字的也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这一点上  后藤老师漫画里的角色名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是绝不会有人取给小孩的  真令人安心呢
