Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.47,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\pos(1664.4,64.4)\c&HC3AC6B&\3c&H968465&}紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.51,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H3B63E7&\3c&H4338AF&\pos(1227.6,285.2)}袜带
