Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:34.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如你所言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,阿童木  不可以跑去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给孩子取自己笔下角色的名字什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到底是种什么心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一辈子都感受不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,紧身裤  不可以跑去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被取了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,乖  是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下半身的样子就像穿着紧身裤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真…可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬小姐  在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,纳德拉小姐的国家有占卜么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:20.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想测测吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,通过向精灵祈祷进行占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  一直嗯嗯嗯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没  因为我是本名出道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,日子很难过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那样的话  现在起用笔名不也挺好的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.84,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,200)\frz282.3\c&HD2BE8F&\3c&HB7AF5F&\pos(444.8,529.6)}掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.71,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,712)}鳞片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.71,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：「鳞片从眼睛里掉出来」有「令人眼前一亮」「恍然大悟」的意思  源自圣经故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一起想想？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.59,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(3.2,153.6)}暗骑士07@3rd
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.59,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自创作者龙骑士07
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.68,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\pos(1870,284)}周刊少年漫画人总编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.68,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\pos(1450.4,390.8)}大和力郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.68,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：音同印刷排版切割
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这啥玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师的笔名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像下周开始就要用这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行么  明明我也跟着一起思考过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是出道前的新人还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(288.4,202)}副总编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(261.2,576.8)}内木理佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：音同腰斩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作家名就是品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就跟商标一样的  突然改变的话会使客人迷惑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  那我去告诉他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他的态度很坚决么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他说「用现在的名字的话日子很难过」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.18,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}人声嘈杂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:32.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是那个吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:36.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有没有奇怪的占卜师在后藤老师那儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作家突然想要改名的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:44.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,背后其实是被这类人洗脑操纵的案例有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作室倒没见过占卜师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有的话那应该就是在家里了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个雾气是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:54.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还真有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,精灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,纳德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来了么  精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  这位精灵先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.53,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,78.4)}参考动画第一话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,跟上次来我家的CEO很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,CEO？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也来测测吗  CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,CEO…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这就是我真正的名字么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,志伟王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.17,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H5A48CD&\frx10\fry342\frz20.03\org(806.4,222.4)\pos(398.4,166.4)}周刊少年漫画人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟迷上奇怪的占卜师  灵能者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而变得奇怪的漫画家有不少人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像是突然开始改名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.30,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frz12.16\pos(667.2,450.8)\c&H9DA3AF&}新名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.30,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz282.1\pos(616,618.4)\c&HA1A5B1&}太郎零式1/6
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对话框里的文本多到异常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.26,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1262.4,876.8)}※不是指柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用富氢水稀释墨水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.47,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1451.2,857.6)\c&H498EA1&}墨汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,发展到最后甚至有人坚信自己是神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而成为了教主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有占卜师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是完全不是什么可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全全全  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后呢  我也想改名了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,改成志伟王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}完全全全全全全全全…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被洗脑的人都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}全全全全…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:46.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,听我说  今天我和纳德拉小姐一起看到精灵先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:47.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,精灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为来的是个很没有气场的精灵先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,纳德拉小姐觉得很可惜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么  很可惜呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  纳德拉小姐说有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便不通过精灵先生来占卜也能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:08.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我和爸爸有个很强的守护灵跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,它一直保护着我们所以没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.26,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(908.8,454.4)\frz34.24\frx36\fry0}13岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:21.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然爸爸不怎么信鬼灵这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个我就试着信信看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我还向精灵先生说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:37.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「今后也请多多关照爸爸和我」了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说  爸爸擅长画画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为…为什么问起这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想起来我还从未看见过爸爸画画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那毕竟是因为我在全力隐瞒着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为不擅长所以不画么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也不能说不擅长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这  我怎么会在这种无聊的地方放不下自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  是很擅长咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,普普通通…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作业  是风景的素描
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗  普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实比普通还是稍微厉害一点…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.46,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz333.7\pos(1041.6,662.4)}分镜素描
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.46,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：标题源自苍树梅的漫画「向阳素描」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,进退两难了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,星期天我要和姬去写生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在想因画得好被姬尊敬的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画得太好的话又会暴露我的职业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要画什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那多半是街道的风景之类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:50.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师您…不是好多年都没画过背景了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说什么傻…傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,风景这种东西  我随时都能画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:57.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您不用担心  不会暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比新手好一点点的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:07.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,刚才的只是热身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下来我要认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,背景什么的就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师您赶快去画角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样下去工作可就完不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哇  这张画得太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这怕是会暴露自己是职业漫画家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就有点伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,若是暴露自己是漫画家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,素描的风景画要上色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又不是水墨画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你问这个干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:42.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,突然想到自从我来了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还一回都没画过彩页呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:55.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说的也是  已经很多年都没登过刊头彩页了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,求你不要往黑白色的原稿上色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这周我们又不是刊头彩页
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(840,148.8)\frz11.42\c&H9EE3F2&\3c&H517175&}艺术学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\frz12.57\pos(921.6,288)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H636B49&}今日！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H435148&\frz11.49\pos(906,365.2)}绘画教室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3F3F3F&\frz7.036\pos(947.6,629.2)\frx4\fry2}招募学生中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs40\c&H72ADD4&\3c&H617574&\frz14.32\pos(1293.2,758.8)}新手  小初高学生
