Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs35\c&H72ADD4&\3c&H617574&\frz13.65\pos(1341.2,893.2)}今日的教师是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz14.04\pos(1275.2,1028.8)}千田奈留{\bord3\fs35\c&H72ADD4&\3c&H617574&}老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.14,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H86CA2F&\3c&H1B1919&\pos(1144,771.2)}职业人士的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.14,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H8507DB&\3c&H3D4859&\pos(481.6,788.8)}姬的崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早知道这样就不该来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么  开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸  您怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我每周做一次志愿者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来这里教小朋友们画画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原  原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道您是来学习绘画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,脸红了  真是不知道他在害羞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道是假借来绘画教室学习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,实则是来见我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这其中有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这件事可要对姬保密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:06.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你的绘画技术已经好到能够教别人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其实…我已经获得过好多次奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了得到姬的崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暂且先舍弃我的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,向她请教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我才是  拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.80,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H3E3B4A&\frz270\pos(188,242.8)}指请教学习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.80,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H3E3B4A&\frz270\pos(1805.6,239.2)}指交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画塑像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我倒是想画能够上色的画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:40.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画得怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:42.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我指的是画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真…真的吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也想你提一些严格的建议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但硬要挑毛病的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比较像是漫画风格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这张就比较像是北斗神拳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果让画漫画的人画素描
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,总是会犯职业病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画得比较像是漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1534.4,230.4)}圣乔治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}注：屠龙者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(74.8,185.6)}青年玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：罗马十二主神之一，类似希腊的军神阿瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(406.4,698.8)}阿里亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(8,576)}注：希腊神话中帮助条赛给他毛线通过迷宫的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是后藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,六条老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您现在是要回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,绘画教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师  难道您偷偷地在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,教别人画画是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做志愿者教别人画画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我太敬仰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:38.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实  职业漫画家的绘画技术真是特别好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果你认为漫画家也擅长画一般的画作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫画好像被人称作是综合艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,既要求能画画又要求能写故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我正是因为不能单凭绘画和写作生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才来画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是您可不能插手姬的画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这可是作业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使您再疼爱她  作弊可是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我并没有这个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是会认真检查的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就因为我是职业漫画家这一原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然让姬陷入到了明明是自己独立完成的画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,却要受到不正当评价的处境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看来只能让她亲眼看到姬独自画画的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才能证明姬的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你星期天有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我希望你能和我一起去动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一  一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这难道是约会的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:45.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后  到了星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和姬一起出门  真是兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有好多动物呢  确实挺让人困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我该怎么做呢  画什么才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬你就画自己喜欢的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.14,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(1112,329.6)\c&H626069&}老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:25.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要画老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉这个约会好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然叫我不要被人发现默默看着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟要是让人看见老师和学生家长一起约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你可要看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这可是姬自己一个人画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊  是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们是来完成老师布置的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师你是因为星期天一个人太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才来动物园是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人家才不寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人家可是在约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来就和「剩女单身婚礼」那种东西一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,约会的对象我可是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他…与我咫尺天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咫尺天涯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们竟然这么不懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师的恋人居然已经不在这个世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师肯定是因为受到了打击才疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才自己一个人约会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要好好观察后再画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你不画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画…画哟  当然画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我对画风景没什么自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才叫姬来的动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像我更不擅长画动物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,它藏在洞里了  看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只能凭想象画了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,凭想象画的话就很像漫画了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从洞里可以看见它的眼睛在放光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老虎能看见我们这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,应该能看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到最后它都还是没能从洞里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这一切你都见证了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是一次美妙的约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,约会真的让人好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明天我会乖乖的  老师你可要振作起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没能画成  真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我画好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,凭想象画好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是看着画的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是看不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我画的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老虎眼中的我和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是凭想象的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不对哦  我可是看着老虎画的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你这都第几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要怎么处理在动物园打高尔夫这个场景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能画动物的人已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:39.25,kakushigoto in 2 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz270\c&H6D6E71&\move(1802.4,200.8,1728,232,0,3864)}好多狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使不用画极其费事的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也能够表现出动物园的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从动物的视角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是老手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,随机应变的能力果然与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.43,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3D3C4D&\pos(659.2,798.4)}在遇到困难时经常使用的一种手法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.31,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(356.8,246.4)\c&H616161&}火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.44,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H616161&\pos(1902.4,382.4)}怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怪兽来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使不直接画出来也能够表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这就是职业人士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉就像是低成本电影一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,装饰起来好羞耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么呢  画得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸可是下了血本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,买来了最贵的画框
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根本就和房子不协调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:18.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但感觉好像在哪里见到过这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.60,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(1112,329.6)\c&H626069&}老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:34.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.60,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H5280DC&\frz1.905\pos(556.8,435.2)}照相纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.60,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\fs50\frz2.3\pos(571.2,614.4)\c&H5EB4E7&}一张1000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.77,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(820.8,971.2)\c&H4E4EA2&}动物RASIA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.77,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自横滨动物园爱称
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:46.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没错  以前我们仨也一起去那拍了这样一张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那副画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:58.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是从她的视角画的吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
