Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:34.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是我被关起来熬夜赶稿  姬可是会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:35.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,房间我已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:36.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,关起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:40.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.02,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\i1\c&H000000&\pos(728,356.8)}即使如此依然轮番上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.02,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\i1\c&H000000&\pos(843.2,664)}住下来了！
